        "    - [Tab Separated Values files]{.accent} (`.tsv`) - similar to CSV but uses tabs instead of commas.\n",
        "    - [Excel files]{.accent} (`.xlsx`) - spreadsheets with complex formulas and formatting.\n",
        "\n",
        ":::{.fragment}\n",
